note: Recon 2M.2 includes metabolite “2,7-decadienoylcoa”, which participates in reactions of fat beta oxidation. Neither MetaNetX nor HMDB include “2,7-decadienoylcoa”, but do include “2,4-Decadienoyl-CoA” which is also participates in fat beta oxidation. “2,4-Decadienoyl-CoA” is not previously in Recon 2M.2.
Both MetaNetX and HMDB include the trans cis but not cis trans isomer.
Both MetaNetX and HMDB include the cis but not trans isomer.
Both MetaNetX and HMDB include the cis but not neutral isomer.
Both MetaNetX and HMDB include the cis but not trans isomer.
